A simple Tab Manager for Chrome that actually works! Allows you to quickly save all currently open tabs against a name of your choice. Shows you a list of all your stored tab groups and you can click on them to open the associated tabs instantly. You can also type "go groupname" in the browser address bar without having to open the extension popup. No data stored in the cloud, all on chrome.storage.local so no security or privacy worries. Enjoy!
